lead_paragraph: The Carolina Panthers ended the regular season with only one loss. And the Panthers will begin their run to the Super Bowl with home-field advantage throughout the NFC playoffs.

headline.print_headline: AP Power Rankings: Panthers End Regular Season at No. 1
